### Genfeed API - Admin Announcements Endpoints
### Broadcast changelog, BIP posts, and AI news to Discord and/or Twitter
### All endpoints require IP whitelist (IpWhitelistGuard)


### Broadcast to Both Discord and Twitter
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/admin/announcements/broadcast
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "We just shipped a major update to the GenFeed AI workflow engine. Check it out!",
  "tweetText": "We just shipped a major update to the GenFeed AI workflow engine. Check it out! 🚀 #genfeedai",
  "channels": ["discord", "twitter"],
  "discordChannelId": "1234567890123456789"
}


### Broadcast to Discord Only
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/admin/announcements/broadcast
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "New changelog: v2.5.0 — improved image generation pipeline and faster rendering.",
  "channels": ["discord"],
  "discordChannelId": "1234567890123456789"
}


### Broadcast to Twitter Only
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/admin/announcements/broadcast
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "AI news: Our new pattern-context engine is now live in production.",
  "tweetText": "AI news: Our new pattern-context engine is now live. #ai #genfeedai",
  "channels": ["twitter"]
}


### Get Announcement History
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/admin/announcements
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
